{"tid":1699715,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"關於三罷 我有小小提議","createTime":"2019-11-08T06:42:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T13:04:12.000Z","uid":43136,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7a4dc62e7f90898028bbea704df6937f23d92d2b","tid":1699715,"uid":43136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T06:42:38.000Z","msg":"為左周同學，為左對抗極權，對抗警暴，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">三罷係短期內最有效嘅方法。</span><br />\n<br />\n我知，可能你會驚，得你自己一個罷，所以我有個提議。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">與其全日罷工，我哋可以先揀下晝罷。<br />\n朝早照常返工，放lunch時好似快閃咁出黎，但係放完lunch唔好番去。</span><br />\n<br />\n以上方法可以當試水溫，一黎可以出黎睇下有幾多人罷工再決定下一部行動，二黎淨係罷半日對公司影響冇咁大，後果都冇咁嚴重，三黎一日內下晝突然少左咁多人返工，效果幾震撼。<br />\n<br />\n如果半日罷工成功嘅話，大家就有動力去全日、多日大罷工。<br />\n<br />\n希望大家都醒覺，香港人要贏，一定要成功咁大罷工。<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"57dd57849fa0bba6eea47436d00cf7cd5be45b52","tid":1699715,"uid":43136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T06:42:56.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"822a835e23a93067e4cc5fca2126e98cc2086ee4","tid":1699715,"uid":43136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T06:43:34.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"985cbaf6ac48aaa851d3d8df7cbd2ab6fbf59c57","tid":1699715,"uid":43136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T06:43:54.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"30db0b65e95837489b7124b69e126c53ae4502b8","tid":1699715,"uid":43136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T06:44:08.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"146c2c1376708696c3d7dfe0c3beb1e1871fac34","tid":1699715,"uid":44870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T06:44:15.000Z","msg":"我覺得會有反效果, 做過覺得安穩大家更加唔想全面罷工"},{"pid":"42229435d286a968faa76c0fe1ff8f998c4b42e2","tid":1699715,"uid":43136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T06:44:20.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6ff08050172985b8b0bfd41945bfc571800f7098","tid":1699715,"uid":43136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-